WEBVTT

00:00:59.000 --> 00:01:02.080
Na katikati ni mama yangu, Marion.

00:01:02.640 --> 00:01:05.656
Alitumwa kwenda kuanza maisha mapya

00:01:05.680 --> 00:01:07.176
katika nchi mpya

00:01:07.200 --> 00:01:08.456
yeye mwenyewe

00:01:08.480 --> 00:01:09.920
akiwa na miaka 12.

00:01:10.920 --> 00:01:12.536
Najua hili;

00:01:12.560 --> 00:01:15.816
Kama Waingereza wasingeruhusu wakimbizi

00:01:15.840 --> 00:01:17.040
mwaka 1940,

00:01:17.800 --> 00:01:20.880
Nina uhakika nisingekuwa hapa leo.

00:01:22.240 --> 00:01:26.360
Bado katika miaka 70, gurudumu limezunguka kuwa kamili.

00:01:26.840 --> 00:01:29.856
Sauti za kuta ambazo zimejengwa,

00:01:29.880 --> 00:01:32.376
siasa za visasi,